1
00:00:00,960 --> 00:00:03,950
Hey, all you viewers out there!

2
00:00:03,950 --> 00:00:07,120
When you're watchin' Fairy Tail, make 
sure to keep the room nice and bright,

3
00:00:07,120 --> 00:00:09,440
and sit back from the screen, 'kay?

4
00:00:10,700 --> 00:00:13,320
Previously on Fairy Tail!

5
00:00:13,590 --> 00:00:15,440
U-U-Uh, oh!

6
00:00:15,440 --> 00:00:20,070
Laxus's Raijin Tribe have come and attacked 
in the middle of the Harvest Festival!

7
00:00:20,070 --> 00:00:23,000
They ruined the Miss Fairy Tail Contest, 
and took the contestants hostage,

8
00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:25,790
and now they've started some battle game!

9
00:00:25,790 --> 00:00:27,210
I have to do something!

10
00:00:27,210 --> 00:00:30,050
Except I happened to be stoned right now!

11
00:02:00,430 --> 00:02:03,650
It seems like there's some 
trouble at Fairy Tail.

12
00:02:03,650 --> 00:02:05,180
What's going on?

13
00:02:05,180 --> 00:02:08,000
Their members are fighting 
amongst each other.

14
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:13,270
It's not just quarreling, they've 
been seriously going at each other!

15
00:02:13,270 --> 00:02:16,590
I hope their big parade, 
Fantasia, will be okay.

16
00:02:22,010 --> 00:02:23,720
Fairy Tail again?

17
00:02:23,720 --> 00:02:26,590
Don't go crazy in the city!

18
00:02:26,590 --> 00:02:27,540
Citizens?

19
00:02:27,790 --> 00:02:34,180
I see. It seems the rules inside the 
rune barriers only affect wizards.

20
00:02:34,180 --> 00:02:35,080
Visitar!

21
00:02:35,760 --> 00:02:36,740
Nab!

22
00:02:36,740 --> 00:02:38,750
Play nice and let yourself get blown away!

23
00:02:38,750 --> 00:02:43,300
If I don't put you to sleep, 
I can't go search for Laxus!

24
00:02:43,550 --> 00:02:46,740
This isn't the time to be 
fighting amongst ourselves,

25
00:02:46,740 --> 00:02:48,270
but if that's the way you want it!

26
00:02:52,740 --> 00:02:53,870
Max!

27
00:02:53,870 --> 00:02:55,830
I've seen through your plans!

28
00:02:55,830 --> 00:02:58,900
You're planning a surprise attack 
using your Sand Magic, aren't you?

29
00:02:59,140 --> 00:03:01,000
Your specialty, Telepathy?

30
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:05,360
But even if you know it's coming, 
you can't dodge my attack, Warren!

31
00:03:07,300 --> 00:03:08,250
Take this!

32
00:03:08,250 --> 00:03:10,290
I told you, I can read your mind!

33
00:03:10,290 --> 00:03:12,670
That's pretty flashy for some festival show.

34
00:03:12,670 --> 00:03:13,450
Here they go again...

35
00:03:13,450 --> 00:03:15,460
What a bunch of troublemakers they are!

36
00:03:17,310 --> 00:03:19,940
Defeat your Friends to Save your Friends!

37
00:03:21,430 --> 00:03:25,000
This is for Mira-chan! Now 
hurry and take defeat like a man!

38
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:27,560
A married man shouldn't be 
lusting after her like that!

39
00:03:27,810 --> 00:03:30,240
Like you should talk, divorcee!

40
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:31,810
Bring it on!

41
00:03:31,810 --> 00:03:34,550
Laki! Yeah, it's the Harvest Festival, but...

42
00:03:34,550 --> 00:03:35,930
What's with the sudden style change?

43
00:03:35,930 --> 00:03:37,270
It looks slutty!

44
00:03:37,270 --> 00:03:39,110
Gunning for the Miss Fairy Tail Contest?

45
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:42,150
All I did was cut my hair, 
and look at all the fuss...

46
00:03:42,150 --> 00:03:44,420
I'm such a <i>bad</i>-girl!

47
00:03:44,420 --> 00:03:45,330
Now I'm mad!

48
00:03:45,330 --> 00:03:46,120
Get her!

49
00:03:50,160 --> 00:03:51,660
There!

50
00:03:54,020 --> 00:03:56,940
Max vs. Warren.  Winner: Warren.

51
00:03:56,940 --> 00:03:59,770
Vistar vs. Nab. Winner: Nab.

52
00:03:59,770 --> 00:04:04,130
Laki took out four, Macao vs. 
Wakaba's battle is in progress.

53
00:04:04,130 --> 00:04:07,240
Enough! Stop this, you foolish children!

54
00:04:07,240 --> 00:04:10,280
Rune traps have been set 
up throughout the city.

55
00:04:10,280 --> 00:04:13,640
And the ones who are trapped 
inside are forced to fight.

56
00:04:13,640 --> 00:04:17,680
That's the Battle of Fairy 
Tail that Laxus talked about.

57
00:04:18,940 --> 00:04:21,320
But why? I don't get it!

58
00:04:23,450 --> 00:04:24,600
Natsu...

59
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:26,490
I wanna join, too!

60
00:04:26,490 --> 00:04:28,260
That's what he's upset about?

61
00:04:28,260 --> 00:04:31,780
What's with this invisible wall?

62
00:04:33,590 --> 00:04:36,200
And what do you plan to do by joining in?

63
00:04:36,200 --> 00:04:38,570
It's a tournament to see who's the strongest!

64
00:04:38,570 --> 00:04:40,630
How is this a tournament?

65
00:04:41,630 --> 00:04:45,630
This is all just Laxus's plan to 
get us to wipe each other out!

66
00:04:46,060 --> 00:04:49,150
Unless we can defeat the Raijin 
Tribe within the time limit,

67
00:04:49,150 --> 00:04:51,600
Erza and the other girls will turn to dust.

68
00:04:51,600 --> 00:04:54,720
Everyone is doing whatever 
they can to prevent that.

69
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:58,100
It'll need something more than our usual way 
of thinking to take control of the situation!

70
00:04:58,510 --> 00:05:02,360
At this rate everyone who was turned 
to stone with crumble into dust.

71
00:05:02,360 --> 00:05:04,530
There won't be any way to restore them.

72
00:05:04,530 --> 00:05:07,610
Laxus acts bad, but he 
ain't gonna go that far.

73
00:05:08,110 --> 00:05:11,370
Yeah, he gets on my nerves, but 
he's a fellow guild member.

74
00:05:11,370 --> 00:05:13,120
It's a bluff, obviously.

75
00:05:13,120 --> 00:05:14,580
Natsu.

76
00:05:14,580 --> 00:05:16,670
This is just a fighting festival!

77
00:05:16,670 --> 00:05:18,820
But then why can't I get out?

78
00:05:18,820 --> 00:05:21,370
I can go through normally!

79
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:25,030
People over 80 years old 
can't pass through...

80
00:05:25,030 --> 00:05:27,270
Does that mean I'm over 80?

81
00:05:27,270 --> 00:05:29,730
I don't think you are, but...

82
00:05:30,500 --> 00:05:34,060
You call Laxus your fellow member?

83
00:05:34,060 --> 00:05:37,280
You don't believe that he'll go that far?

84
00:05:39,060 --> 00:05:42,240
There's 2 hours and 18 minutes left.

85
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:45,190
And there are... 42 people left.

86
00:05:45,430 --> 00:05:51,390
42 people? More than half are 
gone after the infighting!

87
00:05:51,870 --> 00:05:55,120
Go! Purple Rain!

88
00:05:59,320 --> 00:06:02,280
My Smoke Fake. You're getting rusty.

89
00:06:02,280 --> 00:06:06,260
You've always been too soft on people...

90
00:06:08,400 --> 00:06:11,500
The East Forest... The East Forest...

91
00:06:11,500 --> 00:06:16,620
I have to see Poluchka and get a 
potion to cure Erza and the others...

92
00:06:21,520 --> 00:06:22,860
I-It can't be!

93
00:06:23,100 --> 00:06:26,570
Are the runes set up around the entire city?

94
00:06:28,880 --> 00:06:31,650
I will allow no one to break my rules.

95
00:06:33,510 --> 00:06:34,580
Freed!

96
00:06:34,580 --> 00:06:39,580
Laxus should have told you that the 
field of battle was the entire city.

97
00:06:39,580 --> 00:06:43,040
If you're a wizard, then 
fight! Show me your power.

98
00:06:45,310 --> 00:06:47,200
That's the rule.

99
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:50,130
And so...

100
00:06:50,630 --> 00:06:53,440
Damn it, where are those Raijin Tribe?

101
00:06:53,960 --> 00:06:55,430
It's Gray!

102
00:06:58,450 --> 00:06:59,640
Those are Bicslow's...

103
00:06:59,640 --> 00:07:01,030
Yo!

104
00:07:01,140 --> 00:07:03,640
Let's play!

105
00:07:06,820 --> 00:07:08,530
Evergreen!

106
00:07:08,530 --> 00:07:11,600
If you're a Man, then don't take hostages!

107
00:07:11,600 --> 00:07:14,490
Return my sister and the others to normal!

108
00:07:15,610 --> 00:07:18,530
Well, I'm not a man...

109
00:07:22,710 --> 00:07:25,670
I love flowers.

110
00:07:25,670 --> 00:07:28,760
They look so good... on me.

111
00:07:32,370 --> 00:07:35,730
The only thing that's cute 
about you is your name.

112
00:07:36,020 --> 00:07:37,220
Elfman.

113
00:07:39,510 --> 00:07:42,190
Return my sister and the others to normal!

114
00:07:42,900 --> 00:07:46,210
Can you beat me while you're blindfolded?

115
00:07:51,250 --> 00:07:52,700
There you are!

116
00:07:54,240 --> 00:07:58,970
I see! So you can tell where I am by smell.

117
00:07:59,200 --> 00:08:03,450
It's too bad though, because you 
are already inside my Fairy Dust.

118
00:08:04,210 --> 00:08:06,880
Fairy Bomb, Gremlin!

119
00:08:15,400 --> 00:08:17,850
I love statues.

120
00:08:17,850 --> 00:08:23,520
No matter how ugly a monster might be, they 
become a beautiful work of art when turned to stone.

121
00:08:23,770 --> 00:08:26,620
Now, gaze at me.

122
00:08:27,110 --> 00:08:30,550
Give your body up to beauty...

123
00:08:33,570 --> 00:08:38,110
Evergreen vs. Elfman. Winner: Evergreen.

124
00:08:38,110 --> 00:08:40,030
Elfman: Out of commission.

125
00:08:40,280 --> 00:08:42,390
I can't believe Elfman got beat!

126
00:08:43,350 --> 00:08:47,650
Gray's fighting Bicslow! I wanna join in!

127
00:08:47,650 --> 00:08:50,230
Reedus is fighting Freed, too!

128
00:08:50,230 --> 00:08:52,420
The Raijin Tribe has started 
to make their move!

129
00:08:54,180 --> 00:08:55,670
I guess that's it.

130
00:08:56,150 --> 00:08:57,830
Hold it!

131
00:09:00,690 --> 00:09:03,020
Let's settle this fight, man to man!

132
00:09:03,020 --> 00:09:05,030
I mean, man to girl!

133
00:09:06,910 --> 00:09:08,980
I thought you turned to stone.

134
00:09:08,980 --> 00:09:11,610
The magic wore off, and I came after you!

135
00:09:12,120 --> 00:09:16,550
I bet you don't know the tricks this 
man, I mean woman, has up her sleeves!

136
00:09:16,550 --> 00:09:20,470
Do you even have the courage to 
face me like a man, I mean woman?

137
00:09:21,410 --> 00:09:23,120
Whoops!

138
00:09:28,040 --> 00:09:30,780
A fake you made with your magic?

139
00:09:31,640 --> 00:09:35,180
You are a wizard who can make anything 
he paints come to life, after all.

140
00:09:35,630 --> 00:09:40,180
If I hadn't known that, 
I might have been fooled.

141
00:09:42,850 --> 00:09:44,210
Freed?

142
00:09:44,820 --> 00:09:48,720
I'm begging you, don't 
hurt anyone any more...

143
00:09:49,520 --> 00:09:52,780
You aren't that kind of man...

144
00:09:56,380 --> 00:10:00,250
Battle of Fairy Tail... 40 people left.

145
00:10:02,210 --> 00:10:03,950
Reedus was beaten!

146
00:10:04,910 --> 00:10:07,900
I figured Freed could do it! Look at him go!

147
00:10:07,900 --> 00:10:10,680
Is this really the time to be impressed?

148
00:10:10,680 --> 00:10:13,520
Now we can't get any help from Poluchka!

149
00:10:13,520 --> 00:10:14,690
We don't need any.

150
00:10:14,690 --> 00:10:17,340
The whole turning to dust thing is a bluff.

151
00:10:17,970 --> 00:10:21,050
You think I'm bluffing, Natsu?

152
00:10:21,050 --> 00:10:22,640
Laxus!

153
00:10:22,640 --> 00:10:24,060
It's a thought projection!

154
00:10:24,310 --> 00:10:28,190
So why are you still here, Natsu?

155
00:10:28,190 --> 00:10:29,520
I can't get out!

156
00:10:30,240 --> 00:10:31,730
Laxus...

157
00:10:31,980 --> 00:10:36,540
Your members... Well, I guess 
you call them your children.

158
00:10:36,820 --> 00:10:40,280
I bet you can't stand watching your 
children destroy each other, can you?

159
00:10:40,780 --> 00:10:43,450
Natsu and Erza can't join in...

160
00:10:43,450 --> 00:10:47,190
There's no one left who could 
defeat my Raijin Tribe, is there?

161
00:10:48,550 --> 00:10:50,490
Gonna give in?

162
00:10:51,800 --> 00:10:53,570
Gray's still there!

163
00:10:53,570 --> 00:10:55,750
He's about as strong as Natsu!

164
00:10:55,750 --> 00:10:58,050
He ain't gonna lose to no Raijin Tribe!

165
00:10:58,050 --> 00:10:59,740
The same as me?

166
00:10:59,740 --> 00:11:00,900
Him?

167
00:11:00,900 --> 00:11:02,550
But it's the truth!

168
00:11:02,800 --> 00:11:03,950
Gray?

169
00:11:05,290 --> 00:11:08,060
I wouldn't put much faith in that brat.

170
00:11:08,310 --> 00:11:11,270
Don't underestimate Gray, Laxus!

171
00:11:16,440 --> 00:11:18,360
Line Formation!

172
00:11:24,670 --> 00:11:26,560
Not bad, Gray!

173
00:11:26,560 --> 00:11:29,160
Next up, Victory Formation!

174
00:11:29,890 --> 00:11:31,460
What's the matter, Babies?

175
00:11:34,690 --> 00:11:36,220
When did he...

176
00:11:38,630 --> 00:11:40,920
Ice Make Hammer!

177
00:11:42,550 --> 00:11:44,890
X Formation!

178
00:11:49,050 --> 00:11:49,490
What's this?

179
00:11:51,720 --> 00:11:57,250
Part of my Seith Magic is the ability 
to possess the souls of dolls!

180
00:11:57,250 --> 00:12:02,870
Even if you freeze the dolls, I can 
transfer their souls to other bodies!

181
00:12:04,950 --> 00:12:05,960
What?

182
00:12:05,960 --> 00:12:08,120
This guy's gonna be annoying...

183
00:12:17,330 --> 00:12:22,010
Don't you get it? No matter how many 
of my dolls you destroy, it's no use!

184
00:12:22,010 --> 00:12:25,180
Then I'll freeze you directly instead!

185
00:12:26,760 --> 00:12:29,280
Go ahead and try!

186
00:12:29,280 --> 00:12:30,970
What, trying to escape?

187
00:12:32,530 --> 00:12:34,030
Wait!

188
00:12:40,390 --> 00:12:41,690
That bastard...

189
00:12:41,940 --> 00:12:43,450
Where the hell did he go?

190
00:12:43,450 --> 00:12:45,840
Up here, Gray!

191
00:12:46,110 --> 00:12:48,950
What in the world are you up to?

192
00:12:48,950 --> 00:12:52,860
I told you! I want to play 
with strong opponents!

193
00:12:52,860 --> 00:12:56,220
My babies are gettin' all bored recently!

194
00:12:57,650 --> 00:12:58,920
Runes?

195
00:12:58,920 --> 00:13:04,390
Using magic is prohibited for those within 
the barrier until the battle is over!

196
00:13:04,390 --> 00:13:06,090
One of Freed's traps?

197
00:13:06,300 --> 00:13:11,680
Guess a long-distance wizard like 
myself has a bit of an advantage here!

198
00:13:19,190 --> 00:13:24,190
I knew that without your magic, 
you'd be completely helpless!

199
00:13:24,190 --> 00:13:25,980
You think?

200
00:13:29,870 --> 00:13:31,310
Think you can hit me?

201
00:13:38,290 --> 00:13:40,390
That won't cut it, Gray!

202
00:13:49,900 --> 00:13:52,490
Don't, honey. Stand back from the window.

203
00:13:52,490 --> 00:13:53,310
But!

204
00:13:55,650 --> 00:13:59,770
Why that little... And after he 
got hit by my babies like that!

205
00:14:08,920 --> 00:14:15,540
My extra clothing helped cushion against the 
damage... Don't go scaring me like that.

206
00:14:15,540 --> 00:14:19,230
You should wear some heavy 
clothing sometimes, Gray.

207
00:14:21,100 --> 00:14:25,120
Gray is out of commission. 28 people left.

208
00:14:30,780 --> 00:14:32,880
See, didn't I tell you?

209
00:14:32,880 --> 00:14:36,850
Liar! I'm sure that he used some dirty trick!

210
00:14:38,220 --> 00:14:41,510
So who will beat the Raijin Tribe now?

211
00:14:42,100 --> 00:14:43,540
Gajeel will!

212
00:14:43,540 --> 00:14:47,940
Too bad. Doesn't seem 
like he's participatin'.

213
00:14:47,940 --> 00:14:51,750
He doesn't actually give a 
damn about the guild anyway.

214
00:14:51,750 --> 00:14:53,550
Well, I'm still here!

215
00:14:53,550 --> 00:14:56,660
If you can't get out, it 
won't do you any good.

216
00:14:57,390 --> 00:15:00,150
Fine, enough!

217
00:15:01,200 --> 00:15:02,670
I surrender.

218
00:15:02,940 --> 00:15:04,470
Gramps!

219
00:15:04,470 --> 00:15:06,880
Now, stop this Laxus.

220
00:15:08,070 --> 00:15:09,770
Can't do that.

221
00:15:10,070 --> 00:15:15,880
The high and mighty Master of Fairy Tail 
can't go surrendering at a time like this!

222
00:15:16,210 --> 00:15:22,020
But if you insist, then how about you 
give up your position as Master to me?

223
00:15:22,720 --> 00:15:24,630
That's playing dirty, Laxus!

224
00:15:24,630 --> 00:15:27,450
You scared a me, huh?

225
00:15:27,450 --> 00:15:29,410
You fiend...

226
00:15:29,410 --> 00:15:31,860
Was that your goal all along?

227
00:15:31,860 --> 00:15:35,530
It's only one and a half hours 
until the statues crumble.

228
00:15:35,530 --> 00:15:41,870
If you want to retire, use the guild's loudspeakers
and announce it so the whole town can hear.

229
00:15:41,870 --> 00:15:45,870
Say, "I'm giving up my position 
as Master of Fairy Tail to Laxus!"

230
00:15:46,630 --> 00:15:48,960
Think about it well.

231
00:15:48,960 --> 00:15:52,510
Which is more important, your 
position or your friends?

232
00:15:52,510 --> 00:15:54,130
Hold it, damn it!

233
00:15:57,300 --> 00:16:00,480
If you won't fight me, how 
are you the strongest?

234
00:16:00,480 --> 00:16:01,980
How can you be the master?

235
00:16:02,520 --> 00:16:05,200
I don't care about being master.

236
00:16:05,200 --> 00:16:06,510
You're okay with it?

237
00:16:06,510 --> 00:16:11,290
But I cannot entrust Fairy Tail to Laxus!

238
00:16:11,290 --> 00:16:14,570
He doesn't understand the 
weight of the positoin!

239
00:16:14,570 --> 00:16:16,740
He lacks conviction and heart!

240
00:16:17,320 --> 00:16:20,950
But at this rate Lucy and the 
others will turn to dust...

241
00:16:20,950 --> 00:16:23,840
Someone has to defeat 
Laxus and his gang, or...

242
00:16:27,840 --> 00:16:30,200
Gajeel, that's where you were?

243
00:16:30,200 --> 00:16:31,910
Don't eat the dishware!

244
00:16:31,910 --> 00:16:34,220
Are you going to go?

245
00:16:35,400 --> 00:16:37,550
I've got a bone to pick with him.

246
00:16:38,800 --> 00:16:40,990
Just leave him to me.

247
00:16:47,530 --> 00:16:49,720
Are you also 80?

248
00:16:49,720 --> 00:16:51,230
No, obviously!

249
00:16:51,770 --> 00:16:53,570
At about that time...

250
00:16:53,840 --> 00:16:55,320
Gremlin!

251
00:17:00,770 --> 00:17:02,820
So weak...

252
00:17:04,580 --> 00:17:07,170
Stop it, Bicslow! We're your allies!

253
00:17:07,170 --> 00:17:10,380
I'm not on the side of weaklings!

254
00:17:10,380 --> 00:17:12,450
Ain't that right, babies?

255
00:17:17,560 --> 00:17:18,840
Freed!

256
00:17:20,500 --> 00:17:22,170
Alzack...

257
00:17:22,170 --> 00:17:26,570
Thanks to your runes, I've 
hurt my friends too much.

258
00:17:26,940 --> 00:17:30,810
I told myself it was to change 
Bisca back to normal...

259
00:17:37,530 --> 00:17:40,410
Guns Magic! Tornado Shot!

260
00:17:47,060 --> 00:17:49,500
He sliced through the wind magic?

261
00:17:52,040 --> 00:17:54,000
What is this? I can't breathe...

262
00:17:54,900 --> 00:17:58,430
You're using some strange 
magic other than the runes...

263
00:18:00,730 --> 00:18:02,110
Bisca...

264
00:18:03,820 --> 00:18:07,950
Anyone who uses magic inside these 
runes will be deprived of oxygen.

265
00:18:08,570 --> 00:18:12,650
All I did was use runes 
to their fullest effect.

266
00:18:14,810 --> 00:18:19,210
You think there's anyone who can beat 
me under my rules? Me, the creator?

267
00:18:21,060 --> 00:18:25,940
Battle of Fairy Tail.  So, 2 are left?

268
00:18:26,330 --> 00:18:28,560
Only 2 are left?

269
00:18:28,560 --> 00:18:30,660
Why can't you get out either?

270
00:18:30,660 --> 00:18:31,930
Stop copyin' me!

271
00:18:31,930 --> 00:18:32,910
How should I know?

272
00:18:32,910 --> 00:18:35,450
Now I'm hungry, you bastard!

273
00:18:35,450 --> 00:18:37,510
I really don't know!

274
00:18:38,690 --> 00:18:40,020
Two?

275
00:18:40,720 --> 00:18:42,790
Just you two?

276
00:18:42,790 --> 00:18:46,190
And I wasn't even counted?

277
00:18:46,190 --> 00:18:49,220
I have no more wizards left to fight.

278
00:18:49,220 --> 00:18:50,850
I guess that's it...

279
00:18:50,850 --> 00:18:53,800
Oh, well. Guess I better revive Erza.

280
00:18:53,800 --> 00:18:54,850
What?

281
00:18:55,590 --> 00:18:58,360
And I thought I could finally show up Erza...

282
00:18:58,360 --> 00:19:00,280
Hold it!

283
00:19:00,280 --> 00:19:01,740
What are you gonna do?

284
00:19:02,540 --> 00:19:04,470
Won't she melt if I heat her?

285
00:19:04,470 --> 00:19:05,700
You know, the stone shell...

286
00:19:05,700 --> 00:19:07,340
Don't!

287
00:19:07,340 --> 00:19:11,140
Erza and the others have 
turned to stone completely!

288
00:19:11,140 --> 00:19:13,230
We won't know 'till we try, right?

289
00:19:13,230 --> 00:19:15,960
Stop it! You want to kill Erza?

290
00:19:16,350 --> 00:19:17,900
Broil her nice and good...

291
00:19:17,900 --> 00:19:19,470
Are you going to rub her with flames?

292
00:19:19,470 --> 00:19:22,010
Hey buddy, not so frisky.

293
00:19:24,720 --> 00:19:26,510
Shoot, she broke!

294
00:19:26,510 --> 00:19:28,700
Glue, glue! Happy, get the glue!

295
00:19:28,700 --> 00:19:29,650
Aye, sir!

296
00:19:29,650 --> 00:19:31,940
You idiot! You think that'll fix her up?

297
00:19:31,940 --> 00:19:35,210
Use your flames on my iron, and 
we'll weld her back together!

298
00:19:35,210 --> 00:19:36,730
Fools!

299
00:19:38,770 --> 00:19:40,430
I'm sorry! I'm sorry!

300
00:19:40,430 --> 00:19:42,570
I'm sorry, I'm sorry, I'm sorry!

301
00:19:46,910 --> 00:19:48,040
It's hot...

302
00:19:49,520 --> 00:19:51,470
Was it you, Natsu?

303
00:19:51,470 --> 00:19:53,510
What were you trying to do?

304
00:19:53,950 --> 00:19:56,240
Erza's back!

305
00:19:56,240 --> 00:19:57,790
Thank goodness.

306
00:19:57,790 --> 00:19:58,800
But, how?

307
00:19:59,060 --> 00:20:01,160
I don't really know.

308
00:20:01,580 --> 00:20:05,300
Perhaps it's because of my right eye.

309
00:20:07,790 --> 00:20:12,480
I see! The artificial eye must have 
lowered the effect of the magic.

310
00:20:13,030 --> 00:20:15,880
Erza, do you know what's going on?

311
00:20:15,880 --> 00:20:20,360
Yes. Even though I was turned 
to stone, I could hear you.

312
00:20:20,840 --> 00:20:23,620
Go! It's time for a counter attack!

313
00:20:23,950 --> 00:20:25,780
3 remaining.

314
00:20:26,030 --> 00:20:30,630
With me restored, the number 
remaining changed appropriately.

315
00:20:30,630 --> 00:20:32,400
How elaborate.

316
00:20:32,400 --> 00:20:36,210
Those three are Natsu, 
Gajeel, and Erza, right?

317
00:20:36,460 --> 00:20:38,670
4 remaining?

318
00:20:39,480 --> 00:20:40,290
It increased?

319
00:20:40,290 --> 00:20:41,340
Who?

320
00:20:42,400 --> 00:20:45,340
Everyone is still stone... Then who?

321
00:20:47,100 --> 00:20:51,260
There's one more out there, 
remember? Outside of the city.

322
00:20:52,240 --> 00:20:54,430
You don't mean... Him?

323
00:20:54,430 --> 00:20:55,470
No way!

324
00:20:55,470 --> 00:20:57,530
Does this mean he's back?

325
00:20:57,530 --> 00:21:02,470
Looks like the real war is about to 
begin. This is getting interesting.

326
00:21:02,470 --> 00:21:04,190
Who are you talking about?

327
00:21:06,990 --> 00:21:10,330
Another possible candidate for 
the strongest in Fairy Tail...

328
00:21:11,070 --> 00:21:12,440
Mystogan!

329
00:21:14,960 --> 00:21:18,420
Erza's restored and 
Mystogan joins the fray...

330
00:21:18,420 --> 00:21:22,640
Including me, that's the 
top three in Fairy Tail.

331
00:21:23,560 --> 00:21:25,970
Can't be a festival without the best, right?

332
00:21:26,590 --> 00:21:27,690
Then!

333
00:21:27,690 --> 00:21:29,350
You showed up earlier!

334
00:21:29,350 --> 00:21:31,180
That was a fake...

335
00:21:34,040 --> 00:21:36,810
What's up with the outfit, Erza-chan!

336
00:21:36,810 --> 00:21:39,400
Anyway, a bunch of young 
folks from your place

337
00:21:39,400 --> 00:21:42,440
have been fighting around the 
city and causing trouble.

338
00:21:42,440 --> 00:21:45,440
I apologize. It's part of the 
preparations for the grand parade.

339
00:21:45,690 --> 00:21:48,030
That's some strange preparations all right.

340
00:21:48,030 --> 00:21:49,780
Please look forward to it.

341
00:21:49,780 --> 00:21:51,410
Of course!

342
00:21:51,410 --> 00:21:53,330
Try not to fight so much though, 'kay?

343
00:22:00,710 --> 00:22:04,670
How did you return from 
a statue back to normal?

344
00:22:05,190 --> 00:22:09,430
Well, fine by me. It just means I 
get to have fun tormenting you more!

345
00:22:09,430 --> 00:22:10,720
Evergreen!

346
00:22:10,720 --> 00:22:15,430
You really make me angry. Why are 
you the Fairy Queen, Titania?

347
00:22:16,170 --> 00:22:19,690
I am the number one fairy!

348
00:22:25,230 --> 00:22:33,690
That time we laughed, saying "we're both like each other,"

349
00:22:35,090 --> 00:22:43,870
we even kindly overlooked the little lies.

350
00:22:44,700 --> 00:22:49,970
If we lose a place to go back to together, I don't care.

351
00:22:50,200 --> 00:22:58,720
Because I'll protect that smile.

352
00:22:59,100 --> 00:23:03,160
The meetings and partings numerous as the stars in the sky...

353
00:23:03,160 --> 00:23:05,610
All the things I don't want to lose...

354
00:23:05,610 --> 00:23:10,290
Right now I feel like I don't need any of them.

355
00:23:10,290 --> 00:23:15,440
I just want to see you by my side,

356
00:23:15,720 --> 00:23:21,070
all my happiness and sadness.

357
00:23:21,070 --> 00:23:23,550
Let's start from here.

358
00:23:23,550 --> 00:23:26,150
Let's start our tomorrow.

359
00:23:26,150 --> 00:23:30,650
Let's do it like we've just been reborn.

360
00:23:30,650 --> 00:23:36,200
Like flowers blown in a summer wind,

361
00:23:36,200 --> 00:23:44,900
let us bloom brightly in this instant.

362
00:23:56,060 --> 00:23:59,950
Natsu, if you keep baring your stomach, 
your belly button will get stolen!

363
00:23:59,950 --> 00:24:02,250
Huh? You can steal belly buttons?

364
00:24:02,250 --> 00:24:03,910
But Lucy said so!

365
00:24:03,910 --> 00:24:06,490
If you stick out your stomach 
when lightning strikes,

366
00:24:06,490 --> 00:24:09,080
the god of lightning will 
take your belly button away!

367
00:24:09,080 --> 00:24:11,810
But Happy, you don't have a belly button.

368
00:24:13,470 --> 00:24:16,030
Thunder Palace!

369
00:24:16,470 --> 00:24:18,300
Now that you mention it, yeah.

370
00:24:18,890 --> 00:24:22,380
Only rumbling I'm scared 
of is Gramps' grumbling.

371
00:24:22,380 --> 00:24:24,560
Good one. Give him a point.

372
00:24:24,830 --> 00:24:27,080


